00:22:33.360 --> 00:22:35.020 align:middle line:90%
you do perturbation theory.

00:22:35.020 --> 00:22:35.520 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:22:35.520 --> 00:22:39.470 align:middle line:90%


