00:27:24.060 --> 00:27:27.680 align:middle line:84%
So just to be consistent
with the order I wrote there.

00:27:27.680 --> 00:27:31.940 align:middle line:90%
t prime, psi, t prime, x prime.

00:27:31.940 --> 00:27:34.520 align:middle line:84%
So if you know the wave
function at t prime,

00:27:34.520 --> 00:27:39.750 align:middle line:84%
and then, if I integrate this,
you know the wave function.

00:27:39.750 --> 00:27:44.690 align:middle line:84%
So knowing this object
is equivalent to solving

00:27:44.690 --> 00:27:45.780 align:middle line:90%
the system.

00:27:45.780 --> 00:27:50.120 align:middle line:84%
So now we will describe a
way to compute this object.

