by n intervals.

00:29:01.910 --> 00:29:05.030 align:middle line:90%


00:29:05.030 --> 00:29:07.920 align:middle line:84%
So the width of the
interval is delta t

00:29:07.920 --> 00:29:11.840 align:middle line:84%
