prime divided by n.

00:29:11.840 --> 00:29:13.202 align:middle line:90%
So here is delta t.

00:29:13.202 --> 00:29:16.320 align:middle line:90%


00:29:16.320 --> 00:29:19.920 align:middle line:84%
And if we take n go to
infinity, and then this integral

00:29:19.920 --> 00:29:20.700 align:middle line:90%
